@node "SCSI_II" "SCSI_II"


@{b}SCSI II Emulation :@{ub}


    The Atapi SFF 8020 standard is a translation of the SCSI standard
    to the IDE bus .

    The command set is a subset of the original SCSI II CD extension
    command set and some commands are not present.

    To have a better compatibility following SCSI II commands are 
    emulated by our device :

    
    
    
    READ (6)

    MODE SELECT (6)

    MODE SENSE  (6)

    PLAYTRACKINDEX
@endnode

